~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : wemote                                     ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : wrmote [<superuser level>] <message>

   This command allows superusers to emote to various superuser levels 
   though they can only specifically emote to levels equal or less that 
   their own.  Current levels supported are APPRENTICE -> OWNER. If no 
   level is specified it defaults to APPRENTICE which means that all 
   superusers will here it. If for instance the level is specified as 
   OWNER then only users of level GOD will see the message.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : wtell
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
